Package: kolam
Title: Suite of Tools for Creating and Visualizing Kolams
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Han", "Tran", email = "han_tran@eva.mpg.de", role = "cre"),
  person("Bret", "Beheim", email = "bret_beheim@eva.mpg.de", role = "aut"))
Description: A set of tools for processing and studying kolams. This kolam package should 	enable a way to create, draw and analyze kolam drawings. The functionality 		includes possibilities to extract information on kolam from a transcribed kolam in 	form of a .yaml file, the ability to plot kolams given a sequence of gestures or 	to extract information from a kolam object and the ability to compare kolam 		drawings. See the Github page for more information, documentation and examples.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2),
	bezier,
	plyr,
	dplyr,	
	grid,
	RColorBrewer,
	shape,
	stringr,
	yaml
License: GNU AGPLv3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
